;+
; NAME:
;   phase::statistics
;
; PURPOSE:
;   print statistics of a field (does a 2d gaussfit to determine
;   fwhm and sigma), export fwhm or sigma if requested   
;
; CATEGORY:
;   phase
;
; CALLING SEQUENCE:
;   emf->statistics
;
; INPUTS:
